🧠 Paso 1: Subdominios
subfinder -dL domains.txt -all -recursive -o subs.txt
🧠 Paso 2: Subdominios vivos + info útil
cat subs.txt | httpx -status-code -title -tech-detect -o alive.txt
🧠 Paso 3: URLs (histórico + actual)
cat alive.txt | waybackurls | tee wayback.txt

💡 EXTRA PRO:

cat alive.txt | gau | tee gau.txt

Luego:

cat wayback.txt gau.txt | sort -u > urls.txt
🧠 Paso 4: FILTRAR BASURA 🔥
cat urls.txt | grep -Ev "\.jpg|\.png|\.gif|\.css|\.woff|\.ttf|\.svg|\.mp4|\.pdf" > clean.txt
🧠 Paso 5: separar cosas importantes
🔥 Parámetros
cat clean.txt | grep "=" > params.txt
🔥 JS (MUY IMPORTANTE)
cat clean.txt | grep "\.js" > js.txt

👉 Luego:

cat js.txt | while read url; do python3 linkfinder.py -i "$url" -o cli; done
🔥 Endpoints interesantes
cat clean.txt | grep -E "api|v1|v2|v3|graphql|ajax" > api.txt
🚀 4. Ahora lo importante (donde ganas bugs)
🎯 Para Cache Poisoning

Filtra:

cat params.txt | grep -E "cache|redirect|url|next|data|rsc" > cache_targets.txt
🎯 Para XSS
cat params.txt | gf xss

(si tienes gf)

🎯 Para Open Redirect
cat params.txt | grep -E "redirect|url|next|return" 
